      "text": "うん、うまく出来たかも。怜ちゃんから見て\nどうだった？　直した方がいい箇所とか、あったかな？",
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "特にないわよ。そもそも私が今の千紗に教えられること\nなんてないわ。あっても個人的な意見を言うくらいよ",
      "startTime": 15.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ～、それ何度か言ってくれてるけど、怜ちゃんに\n比べたら、私まだまだだよ？　もっと習いたいよ～",
      "startTime": 24.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
